1:05:53.865 --> 1:05:56.435
We’d like to conclude 
with these greetings 


1:05:56.435 --> 1:06:00.000
from northeastern Bolivia, 
in a region called Beni. 


1:06:01.407 --> 1:06:06.000
This area has a publisher ratio 
of 1 Witness to 426 people. 


1:06:07.145 --> 1:06:11.883
Their territory consists 
mainly of rivers and jungles. 


1:06:11.883 --> 1:06:15.020
The approximately 350 publishers 


1:06:15.020 --> 1:06:18.823
in the cities of Riberalta 
and Guayaramerín 


1:06:18.823 --> 1:06:22.293
need to be innovative to reach 
all corners of their territory. 


1:06:22.293 --> 1:06:24.296
For example, 


1:06:24.297 --> 1:06:27.800
under the direction of the local branch, 
a Witness pilot 


1:06:27.800 --> 1:06:30.903
flies brothers to isolated populations. 


1:06:30.903 --> 1:06:33.138
In other cases, some communities 


1:06:33.138 --> 1:06:35.606
located on the banks of rivers 
are reachable 


1:06:35.607 --> 1:06:37.610
only by boat. 


1:06:37.610 --> 1:06:41.313
Thus, preaching trips by boat 
are arranged from time to time. 


1:06:41.313 --> 1:06:44.483
Some trips last well over a month. 


1:06:44.483 --> 1:06:48.120
But some parts of the territory 
can be reached by motorcycle. 


1:06:48.120 --> 1:06:50.322
The brothers and sisters travel 


1:06:50.322 --> 1:06:53.000
up to four hours 
to cover such territories.


1:06:54.693 --> 1:06:59.631
The brothers and sisters in Beni 
send their warm love, and so do we, 


1:06:59.632 --> 1:07:02.902
to all of you around the world. 


1:07:02.902 --> 1:07:07.540
Rocky, I’d like to thank you for doing 
the heavy lifting for me during this program.


1:07:07.540 --> 1:07:09.275
You’re a good brother, 
you know that?


1:07:09.275 --> 1:07:10.275
My privilege.


1:07:10.275 --> 1:07:11.410
He’s a good brother. 


1:07:11.410 --> 1:07:14.080
And this is JW Broadcasting 


1:07:14.080 --> 1:07:26.577
in Brooklyn, New York.

